track.name: Survival Of The Fittest
comments:
It's unexpected changes and elusive form and the 'Out', free playing and call and response soling make this just wonderful to listen to and follow.
One of the great, great Jazz performances
Muy buen desarrollo del tema, una alta perfomance.

Survival of the fittest is a fitting example of the survival of the fittest form of musical expression against all odds and Herbie is a wonderful example of the mastery and production of jazz which is the highest form of musical expression.
